'''Carlens Arcus''' (born 28 June 1996) is a Haitian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[right-back]] for [[Ligue 1]] club [[Angers SCO|Angers]] and the [[Haiti national football team|Haiti national team]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://haitiantimes.com/haitis-wins-against-suriname-and-now-advances-to-caribbean-final-rounds-7362/ |title=Haiti's wins against Suriname and now advances to Caribbean Final Rounds |editor=Nere, Enock |date=5 August 2014 |publisher=Haitian Times |accessdate=25 July 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725115414/http://haitiantimes.com/haitis-wins-against-suriname-and-now-advances-to-caribbean-final-rounds-7362/ |archive-date=25 July 2015 |url-status=dead }}</ref>

==Club career==
When Arcus was about 15–16 years of age, he travelled to [[São Paulo]], Brazil, and played for a [[Campeonato Brasileiro Série D|Série D]] club, where he learned [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]]. In 2014, he returned to Haiti and played for top-tier [[Racing CH|Racing Club Haïtien]] and then for Club Sportif Saint-Louis of the second division.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lenouvelliste.com/lenouvelliste/article/149783/Un-natif-dHaiti-considere-comme-lavenir-dun-club-de-lelite-du-foot-francais |title=Un natif d'Haïti considéré comme l'avenir d'un club de l'élite du foot français |editor=Legupeterson, Alexandre |date=10 September 2015 |publisher=Le Nouvelliste |accessdate=18 July 2016}}</ref>

Arcus played for [[ES Troyes AC|Troyes]] in [[Ligue 1]] in 2015,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lest-eclair.fr/sport-dans-l-aube/estac-qui-es-tu-carlens-arcus-ia26b0n344085 |title=Estac / Who are you Carlens Arcus? |editor=Matten, Ludovic |date=11 February 2015 |publisher=L'est-Éclair |accessdate=25 July 2015}} {{in lang|fr}}</ref><ref>[http://www.hpnhaiti.com/site/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=16265:haiti-foot-transfert-de-nouveaux-contrats-europeens-pour-les-haitiens&catid=4:sport&Itemid=12 Haiti Press Network - Haïti-Foot-Transfert : De nouveaux contrats européens pour les Haitiens] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924031640/http://www.hpnhaiti.com/site/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=16265:haiti-foot-transfert-de-nouveaux-contrats-europeens-pour-les-haitiens&catid=4:sport&Itemid=12 |date=24 September 2015 }} {{in lang|fr}}</ref><ref>[https://www.msn.com/en-us/sports/soccer/carlens-arcus/player/sp-id-80302000000209171 MSN Sports - Carlens Arcus]</ref> until signing with [[Lille OSC|Lille]] in 2016.<ref name="Tribune">{{cite web |url=http://tribunesports.net/mercato-losc-rony-lopes-carlens-arcus-signent-an/ |title=Mercato : LOSC, Rony Lopes et Carlens Arcus signent un an |editor=Mabouong, Eitel |date=9 July 2016 |publisher=Tribune Sports |accessdate=18 July 2016 |archive-date=13 October 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013092219/http://tribunesports.net/mercato-losc-rony-lopes-carlens-arcus-signent-an/ |url-status=dead }}</ref>

On 23 June 2022, Arcus signed a three-year contract with [[SBV Vitesse|Vitesse]] in the Netherlands.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Vitesse|url=https://www.vitesse.nl/nl/nieuws/detail/9606/carlens-arcus-versterkt-vitesse-en-tekent-driejarig-contract|title=CARLENS ARCUS VERSTERKT VITESSE EN TEKENT DRIEJARIG CONTRACT|date=23 June 2022|access-date=23 June 2022|language=nl}}</ref>

On 27 June 2024, Arcus signed for Ligue 1 club [[Angers SCO|Angers]] on a two-year deal.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.angers-sco.fr/carlene-arcus-signe-au-sco-pour-2-ans/|trans-title=Carlens Arcus signs with SCO for 2 years!|title=Carlens Arcus signe au SCO pour 2 ans!|website=www.angers-sco.fr|language=French|date=27 June 2024|accessdate=27 June 2024}}</ref>

